<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Yellow Search Engine ("we," "our," or "us") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting it through this Privacy Policy. This document explains how we handle your information when you use our search engine.

1. Information We Collect

When you use Yellow Search Engine, we may collect:

Search queries you enter to provide relevant results.

Technical data such as your IP address, browser type, operating system, and general location (country/region).

Usage data such as the pages you visit, time spent, and how you interact with the search engine.

We do not collect personally identifiable information (such as name, email, or phone number) unless you voluntarily provide it through optional features (e.g., creating an account or subscribing to updates).

2. How We Use Information

We use collected information to:

Deliver accurate and relevant search results.

Improve the performance, security, and functionality of the search engine.

Prevent abuse, fraud, or illegal activities.

Analyze trends and usage patterns to enhance user experience.

3. Cookies and Tracking

Yellow Search Engine may use cookies or similar technologies to:

Remember your preferences (such as language or region).

Measure site performance and usage analytics.

You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but some features may not work properly.

4. Data Sharing

We do not sell or trade your personal data. Information may only be shared in the following cases:

With service providers who help us operate the search engine (e.g., hosting, analytics).

If required by law, legal process, or government request.

To protect the rights, safety, or security of our users and services.

5. Data Retention

We only retain collected data for as long as necessary to provide and improve our services. Logs and search data may be anonymized or deleted after a set period.

6. Your Rights

Depending on your location, you may have rights to:

Access the data we hold about you.

Request correction or deletion of your data.

Object to or restrict certain processing.

Opt out of analytics or tracking.

Requests can be made by contacting us at privacy@yellowsrch.com.

7. Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your information against unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission or storage is 100% secure.

8. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted here with a revised "Last updated" date.

9. Contact Us

If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:

Yellow Search Engine
Email: privacy@yellowsrch.com</p>
